 Jamieson said multiple patients were treated at the scene. He said a blind cat was also treated at the scene by Rescue Care emergency officials. 

 

 Jamieson said the cat is alive.

 

 
  
 
 

 

 At this stage, the cause of the fire is unknown. Police will be investigating further.

 

 
  
  
